## Why GPL v3?

This app embeds or bundles **Fairy-Stockfish** / **Stockfish** (GPL v3 chess engines).
Linking or combining with GPL software requires distributing this app under GPL v3
and providing corresponding source code.

## Commercial sale

You **may sell** this app (Mac App Store, your website, etc.) under GPL v3.
Buyers receive the same rights: run, modify, and redistribute the software.
You must provide source code to users who receive the binary — typically via
a public Git repository and/or a "Source code" link in the app.

See also: [Stockfish license FAQ](https://stockfishchess.org/about/)
